history.content:
Hey there! If you’re looking to work on an interesting summer project, check out MathPro! We’re a non-profit group working to advance online education, and we’re looking for students with experience in Python to join our team. Watch our demo video linked below to get an idea of our mission. Fill out the form below if you’re interested in hearing more!

 

Demo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhszR-n12ao

Form: https://forms.gle/46XBwryVQfQxY9wk9
